author: Screen Junkies
description:
It’s time for the ultimate cash-grab / showdown: Freddy vs. Jason! These two horror icons clash in the silliest, least scary movie since Scary Movie. Ah well, at least Hollywood learned their lesson and never resorted to cheap team-up films again, right? Right???

Shout-out to Zack Ward for making another cameo!
